general.name: mastarall
general.description:
This file has 4 extensions: GOODSTARS, GOODVISITS, ALLSTARS, ALLVISITS.
Extension 1 (GOODSTARS): Summary table for stars that have at least one high quality visit spectrum.
Extension 2 (GOODVISITS): Summary table for all of the good visits of the good stars.
Extension 3 (ALLSTARS): Summary table for all stars that have been observed at least once, regardless of the quality of the data.
Extension 4 (ALLVISITS): Summary table for all of the visits of all of the stars.
general.naming_convention: mastarall-[ver1]-[ver2].fits, where [ver1] is the version of the MaNGA Data Reduction Pipeline (mangadrp) and [ver2] is the version of the MaStar post-processing pipeline (mastarproc). These pipelines are used to reduce the data and produce this file.
